 mana that you have at the time. THAT would be worth the skill,time,invested in all the points to get it.NO way would that be over powering. If keeping Manaburn the way it is,make it be 1.0-3.0cast time.If it takes all your mana,what further use do you have when oom? How would that be overpowering?I dont see the reason why to have a 6 second cast time.<br><br> This skill NEEDS to be looked at and retuned.Its just silly how the damage is random no matter how much mana,buffs,pets you have on.<br><br>Master Raistin of the Nexus<br>60 Wizard Veeshan<br>Fires of Heaven<br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uraistin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raistin</A> at: 12/25/01 10:36:55 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufilanfyretracker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Filan Fyretracker</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/25/01 11:54:43 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://pages.cthome.net/filanwizard/wtcsmall.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What Manaburn is/isnt..</span><hr size=1> 8k is pretty impressive to me. =p <p><center><a href="mailto:filan@snet.net"><img src="http://pages.cthome.net/filanwizard/filansig3.jpg" border=0></a><br><i>Join SI, see interesting places, meet interesting creatures and see Fallon get killed by them</i></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufreonsmurf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FreonSmurf